    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173000/extras/6fd6c137cdf83ccc2f78d351014cd689.avif?t=1758137734\" width=539 height=136 /></span><br>In Happies: Amber Falcon, a 2d hand-painted side-scrolling game, you take control of Happies, eternally happy little people who are about to explore the new and dangerous world in a hot air balloon. But your happiness will be challenged by a disaster of cosmic proportions.<br><br>On board the Amber Falcon, you were forced to evacuate your planet and face the dangers of an unknown world after a mysterious crash landing. You will avoid obstacles and traps while collecting &quot;enerbees&quot; - alien fireflies that power up your balloon.<br><br>Explore unknown locations and ancient artifacts. Collect resources to repair your ship in 10 story missions and countless free levels that take you across many diverse environments.<br><br>The Happies is suitable for beginners and children as well as experienced players. It offers 3 different difficulties for everyone to enjoy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173000/extras/099a49922a25ef5b65ad2effce2252cd.avif?t=1758137734\" width=539 height=160 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>15 playable characters<br></li><li>15+ unlockable balloons<br></li><li>10+ unlockable baskets<br></li><li>10 story levels<br></li><li>10+ free levels<br></li><li>hand painted art style<br></li><li>30 unlockable archievements<br></li><li>3 difficulties</li></ul>",
